   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0359"/><hi rend="pre-print">Gruss aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb20650">Thusis</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS00048772X_0360"/>Hn <hi rend="latintype">Gustav Schwarzkopf</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207296"><hi rend="latintype">I. Tiefer Graben 23</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="HS00048772X_0359"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04523-1"/><date>Heute</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04523-1">Der Poststempel datiert den Versand auf den <date>20. 8. 1900</date>. Aus dem <rs type="work" ref="#pmb33243">Tagebuch</rs> geht hervor, dass das <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90119">Schlappiner Joch</rs> bereits am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1900-08-19" subtype="date-only"/> überquert wurde, also dürfte die Karte an diesem Tag geschrieben worden sein.</note> <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind wir um 4 <unclear>a</unclear>ufge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tanden und 
               haben das <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90119"><hi rend="latintype">Schlappiner</hi> Joch</rs> über<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>etzt,
      um in die <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs> zu gelangen.</p><p><date>Morgen</date> fahren wir
      nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>ArthSchn</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb10863"/>Herzl. Ihr <signed>Richard</signed></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="3"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb11910"/><signed>Alfr. Kerr</signed></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="4"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb11485"/>Herzl. Gruß
               <signed>Dr. Goldmann</signed></p></div>
      </body>
